# Tier-3 / G4 — tinyproxy FQDN allowlist (FilterDefaultDeny Yes => only these match).
# POSIX-extended regex, anchored, matched against the CONNECT host (FilterExtended Yes).
#
# Hosts the agent needs:
#   api.anthropic.com  — the Anthropic API (inference). REQUIRED at runtime.
#   *.anthropic.com    — regional/edge API + telemetry hosts under the same domain.
#   *.claude.com       — Anthropic's OAuth/auth + platform domain. REQUIRED for
#                        `claude auth login` and OAuth token REFRESH: the login flow runs
#                        on claude.com with a platform.claude.com callback (NOT
#                        anthropic.com). Confirmed on the first real login run (the proxy
#                        returned 403 until this was added). Operator-approved widening
#                        (still Anthropic-owned). Without it the agent fails closed when
#                        its session expires (must re-login).
#
# Everything else is denied by FilterDefaultDeny. Review the proxy Connect log
# (/var/log/tinyproxy/agent-proxy.log) and tighten if a host turns out unnecessary.

^api\.anthropic\.com$
^([a-z0-9-]+\.)*anthropic\.com$
^([a-z0-9-]+\.)*claude\.com$
